		<br><br><br>
		<p style = "font-size: 75px; color: white; text-align: center; text-shadow: 2px 2px 10px black;"> Thank you to our sponsors!</p>
		</div>

		<div style="clear: both; height: 8px; width: 100%; background-color: #2C3449">  </div>

		<div id = "sponsors-container" style="margin: 2%; text-align: center;">

			<div id = "sponsors-title-container">
				<h1>Our 2019-2020 Sponsors</h1>
			</div>

			<div id = "sponsors-list-container">
				<div>
					<a href="https://www.ams.ubc.ca/">	
